      <title>诺和诺德股价下跌，欧洲股市遭遇 9 月以来最糟糕的一周</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/european-stocks-set-for-the-biggest-weekly-slide-since-september</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲股市出现三个多月来最大单周跌幅，丹麦制药商诺和诺德股价下跌 21%，此前一项研究显示其减肥药物试验结果不尽如人意。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/european-stocks-set-for-the-biggest-weekly-slide-since-september</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Dec 2024 08:12:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>关税风险和美联储放缓宽松步伐导致油价周线下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-december-20</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于投资者权衡美联储降息步伐放缓以及当选总统唐纳德·特朗普威胁对欧盟国家征收关税（除非它们购买更多美国石油和天然气），原油价格本周下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-december-20</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Dec 2024 23:31:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
